name: Vinyl Tee
description:
The Voltage Expedition SQUARE NECK Collection -- "Dare to be Square!"--
The "Music Inspired. Passion Driven" Tee, Square Neck - Vinly Edition

This specific design also says "Electronic Dance Music" across the top of the chest, for those that really love the EDM scene and need something to show your support and love for the genre. Typical EDM tees carry some sort of dumb drug slogan related to the scene. Our brand is as real as the music is, we strive for the best quality along with the best intentions.
(*Our brand does not support the drug culture that is normally known for in the EDM scene, we strive to stay away from that and create a positive message to all EDM enthusiasts.)

This tee is part of the Vinyl Edition Collection which features a unique vinyl design on every tee. This is also a very motivational tee that we stand by 100%, its for those that are Inspired by music in their everyday lives. And for those that are driven by passion for what they do by working harder and making their lives more fulfilling. 

Ready to be unique? Have your own style? Add the square neck to your collection!
Our Vinyl Edition Collection features a unique vinyl design on the tee, everyone knows the ultimate symbol for music and dj'ing, and that is the vinyl. It started it all!


The square neck is a VERY UNIQUE product, never before seen in any other markets out there! The square neck design is VERY COMFORTABLE around the neck, you can hardly notice the NECKLINE when you are wearing the square neck tee. A very good quality made, tight fitting, unique t shirt. 

Wear it by itself or under a dress shirt, be unique, be comfortable!

The Square neck tee is a PATENT PENDING product crafted for the Voltage Expedition Square neck lineup in collaboration with Certified Dress Code, LLC. 

This tee is also Dryer friendly and comes preshrunk, no shrinkage expected!

4.5 oz. 100% cotton 30/1's fine knit tee/PRESHRUNK. 
**Model is wearing a size Medium. 
**Our model is 5'11 with a 32 waist and 32 inseam.
**PRESHRUNK FOR ULTIMATE COMFORT

name: PURE Electronic Dance Music
description:
The Voltage Expedition "Pure Electronic Dance Music" Tee
Crew Neck - Black (Unisex) 

If Electronic Dance Music is the only type of music that runs through your veins day in and day out then you are strictly Pure EDM! Show your love for EDM and share it with the rest of the world by using #PureEDM.

It also has our famous 'do anything you want to" slogan right underneath the EDM graphic. We use this phrase as inspiration to show that anything is possible if you work hard at it. Being that EDM is finally making a comeback, it is the DJ's who are working harder than ever to supply us with the best dance music ever!

We designed this for the ultimate EDM enthusiast, be it man or woman we had it printed on Extra Small sizes and all the way up to X-Large. This tee is originally made for the structure of a man, but with the sizing options it looks great on woman as well. 

**4.5 oz. 100% cotton 30/1's fine knit. 
**Model is wearing a size Medium
** Our model is 5'11 with a 32 waist and 32 inseam.
** Expect a 5% shrinkage after wash and dry.

Music Inspired - Passion Driven

name: Movement of Music Tee
description:
The Voltage Expedition "MOVEMENT OF MUSIC" T-Shirt
White V-Neck with big red Play Button graphic.

If you are passionate about creating music or even just listening to all types of music, this is the tee for you!

This T-Shirt has the 3 music genres "Techno, Hip-Hop & Trance" printed on it. These genres have been collaborating together to make electronic dance music stand out again in the western parts of the world. It's usually unlikely that Hip Hop culture would collaborate with the dance culture, but something is happening all around the world and music is influencing people on a different level. This is why we called this tee "movement of music" due to the change that music has undergone in the last couple of years.

Very comfortable and very light fabric


4.5 oz. 100% cotton 30/1's fine knit tee/PRESHRUNK. 
**Model is wearing a size Small.
**Our model is 5'11 with a 32 waist and 32 inseam.
**Dryer friendly, item is PRESHRUNK and expect no shrinkage after wash.

Music Inspired - Passion Driven

name: Do anything Tee
description:
The Voltage Expedition "do anything you want to" tee. 
White V-Neck

The tee has our brand name printed vertically across half the tee, and the other half says 'do anything you want to". Very simple and to the point, still inspired by our passion for design and for the love of music. 

This is our slogan and we believe that anything is possible if you set your mind to it. If you enjoy it make a career out of it, and you'll never work another day in your life. 
We use this phrase as inspiration to show that anything is possible if you work hard at it. 

When we decided to start up our brand we had obstacles to overcome, once we did we realized that the only way that it was possible was because we believed! We do what we are passionate about and what drives us is the music. If we did it, then you can do anything you want to as well!
